title: Will Entriken with EGLs as a core dev
body:
To provide Will Entriken with 1.5M EGLs at 0xd859d7d8603D2dAb768D679eEEC25930C8FC59C1. 

This will require the multi-sig holders to approve such a transaction. 

Discussion: https://forum.egl.vote/t/proposal-to-provide-william-entriken-with-funds-from-the-core-dev-dao/31?u=eleni

Will is best known for being the ERC-721 (NFTs) lead author since 2018. In addition, he has reviewed/worked on: 0xcert Framework, Nightfall, Solidity, MLB Champions, has responsibly published vulnerabilities against Compound Finance (token prices can change faster than specified) and Aion (can steal anyone's tokens) and reviews interoperability standards, ERC-165, ERC-1167. His work was sponsored in part by the Ethereum Foundation.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/fulldecent?ref_src=twsrc%5Egoogle%7Ctwcamp%5Eserp%7Ctwgr%5Eauthor
Website: https://phor.net/
